headline: International Paper outlines 2027 vision, DS Smith integration plans
summary: “We think we can transform this company,” said CEO Andy Silvernail during an investor day. IP previewed more cost-cutting ahead, plus an estimated $1.9 billion in capital expenditures per year through 2027.
